title: Marvel's Secret Invasion (Chronology)
description:
Marvel's Complete* Secret Invasion event in what seems to be the best Chronological order. Source is included.


* Not included are the Marvel Digital Comic entries as they were just side stories with no bearing on the actual plot. And impossible to find for me.

NOTE: Recommend that you skip any issues marked "Flashback" on the list if you want to be completely surprised. You can always read them later.
